doctor

Class PatientConnect

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.Window
      • doctor.PatientConnect

  • public class PatientConnect
extends Window
    A GUI that allows either (1) creating a new patient record (i.e. instantiate a AddNewPatient, or (2) looking up a returning patient (i.e. instantiate a ReturningPatientSearch). This window will load if Login instance closes after a successful login.
